OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,FA significant number of children
OL,8,Facross Wales are being denied their
OL,9,Fright to an education, according to a
OL,10,FSenedd committee report.
OL,12,FFamilies in Wales have told the
OL,13,FChildren, Young People and Education
OL,14,FCommittee that children and young
OL,15,Fpeople with additional learning needs
OL,16,For disabilities are being 'let down by
OL,17,Fdecision-makers at the most crucial
OL,18,Ftime in their lives.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/15
