OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,FThe committee heard evidence from
OL,8,Ffamilies struggling to access both
OL,9,Finclusive education and suitable
OL,10,Fchildcare support, with the report
OL,11,Fsaying too many mainstream settings
OL,12,Fare not meeting the needs of children
OL,13,Fand young people who are being treated
OL,14,Fas "square pegs in round holes", with
OL,15,Fno adjustments being made to enable
OL,16,Fthem to fully participate in school
OL,17,Flife.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
