OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,FThe report found that an inconsistent
OL,8,Fprovision means there is a postcode
OL,9,Flottery in Wales, especially for those
OL,10,Faccessing Welsh-medium education and
OL,11,Fchildcare, while where good provision
OL,12,Fexists, it is because of the
OL,13,Fdetermination of individuals, not a
OL,14,Fstructural approach.
OL,16,FThe committee is now calling on the
OL,17,FWelsh Government to respond to its
OL,18,Ffive key conclusions and 32
OL,19,Frecommendations following the year-
OL,20,Flong inquiry.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
