OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,FBetsan Gower Gallagher, mum to twin
OL,8,Fseven-year-old girls with autism, gave
OL,9,Fevidence to the committee to be her
OL,10,Fchildren's voice.
OL,12,F"This inquiry is so important to
OL,13,Fparents like me because my children
OL,14,Fare non-verbal, but this gives them a
OL,15,Fvoice," she said.
OL,17,F"My children have highly complex needs
OL,18,Fbut it's an endless battle to get the
OL,19,Fsupport that we're entitled to. We
OL,20,Fhave to fight and fight for even the
OL,21,Fbasics, like an education.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
