OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,F"And there's no childcare support in
OL,8,Four area that can facilitate my
OL,9,Fchildren's needs over summer ` even
OL,10,Factivities that are advertised as
OL,11,Finclusive don't have the facilities to
OL,12,Fsupport us.
OL,14,F"We want to do the best for our
OL,15,Fchildren ` they are so special and
OL,16,Fradiate joy and love ` but we're
OL,17,Fexhausted from the system working
OL,18,Fagainst us."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
