OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,F"We wouldn't be doing our job if we
OL,8,Fdidn't take that and put forward the
OL,9,Fstrongest possible case to the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment for what needs to change `
OL,11,Fthat's what we set out in this report.
OL,12,FIt's the structure that's letting them
OL,13,Fdown, not individual teachers or
OL,14,Fchildcare staff who do their best
OL,15,Fdespite it.
OL,17,F"But this piece of work will not stop
OL,18,Fthere. We will keep a very close eye
OL,19,Fon the actions that are taken and how
OL,20,Fthey are making a difference on the
OL,21,Fground for the rest of the Senedd term.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/15
