OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,F"We can't fail our young people any
OL,8,Fmore. You only get one chance at an
OL,9,Feducation, and it should be the best
OL,10,Fchance."
OL,12,FThe report's five key conclusions:
OL,14,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"Disabled children and young people
OL,16,Fhave a fundamental right to access
OL,17,Feducation and we are committed to
OL,18,Fbreaking down barriers so that all
OL,19,Flearners can reach their full
OL,20,Fpotential.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/15
