OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,F"Our education reforms and our Early
OL,8,FChildhood Play, Learning and Care Plan
OL,9,Fare aimed at achieving an inclusive
OL,10,Fsystem that works for all learners and
OL,11,Freduces inequalities. We will continue
OL,12,Fto work across government and with the
OL,13,FDisability Rights Taskforce to listen
OL,14,Fto families, disabled children and
OL,15,Fyoung people to ensure their voices
OL,16,Fare heard as we consider this work
OL,17,Falongside the Senedd committee's
OL,18,Freport and recommendations."
