OL,7,FJames Radcliffe, Wales' external
OL,8,Faffairs manager for the National
OL,9,FAutistic Society, said: "Autistic
OL,10,Fchildren and their families need to
OL,11,Fget support at the right time, and
OL,12,Fgood childcare providers can help
OL,13,Fdeliver this.
OL,15,F"Delays in accessing suitable support
OL,16,Fcan exacerbate problems, cause
OL,17,Funnecessary stress for parents, and
OL,18,Fharm the life chances of children.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/15
