OL,3,CChildren with ALN and disabilities in
OL,4,CWales 'let down' over 'postcode
OL,5,Clottery'
OL,7,F"Schools desperately need more support
OL,8,Fto effectively put in place the ALN
OL,9,Freforms, so we welcome the inclusion
OL,10,Fof our concerns in the reports'
OL,11,Ffindings. We back the call to ensure
OL,12,FIndividual Development Plans (IDPs)
OL,13,Fare not being denied to children due
OL,14,Fto resource constraints."
OL,16,FMs Badjie also highlighted how one in
OL,17,Ffive teachers of the deaf have been
OL,18,Flost in Wales since 2011.
