OL,7,FShe said: "We are greatly encouraged
OL,8,Fby the committee's recommendation
OL,9,Fwhich calls on the Welsh Government to
OL,10,Fset up a clear plan to address gaps in
OL,11,Fteachers of the Deaf numbers.
OL,13,F"It is now crystal clear to the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment what they must do to make
OL,15,Fsure every deaf child gets the support
OL,16,Fthey need. We look forward to the
OL,17,Fopportunity of working with them,
OL,18,Falong with local authorities and the
OL,19,Fhealth boards."
